ai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738910/extras/Bosses.png?t=1736589114\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight unique boss battles that occur during certain waves. Each boss battle comes with unique mechanics that keep you on your toes. Defeating a boss(Stone Golem, Witch, etc.) will grant the player guaranteed loot. But get defeated by them and your run comes to an end. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738910/extras/Untitledvideo-MadewithClipchamp4-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1736589114\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738910/extras/Armors.png?t=1736589114\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Armor galore! More than one hundred pieces of armor that you can choose from (Common, Rare, Epic, and Legendary). Each armor piece has its own unique set of stats that the player can benefit from.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738910/extras/Choices__1_.png?t=1736589114\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Clearing a wave gives the player the opportunity of buying stats or spells. There are hundreds of buffs and several spells that each character can choose from(Thunder, Beams, Shockwaves, Blackhole, etc.). But beware there is a limit in the amount of spells that can be learnt, so pick wisely what spells you want to have in your arsenal.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738910/extras/ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1736589114\" /></p></li></ul>","developers":["OneCodeStudios"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738910/header.jpg?t=1736589114","is_free":false,"linux_r